    "The task is to perform automated concept recognition using the Human Phenotype Ontology and extract all Human Phenotype Ontology concepts found in the text.",
    "Include the HPO ID of the concepts you find in the result.The first three prompts direct the model to 'extract' artefacts from the provided text.",
